childAltar.hintText: 3 Spiritual Stones found in Hyrule...^$0Shadow Temple...^$1Forest Temple...^$2Water Temple...^$oYe who may become a Hero...&The path to the future is open...

adultAltar.hintText: An awakening voice from the Sacred&Realm will call those destined to be&Sages, who dwell in the five temples.^$8Deku Tree...^$3Jabu-Jabu's Belly...^$4Link's Pocket...^$5Fire Temple...^$6Spirit Temple...^$7Dodongo's Cavern...^$lThe awakened ones will await&for the Hero to find %gGreg%w.^$bAnd the %revil one%w's key will be&provided by Zelda once %r5&Spiritual Stones and Medallions%w&are retrieved.^$kTogether with the Hero of Time,&the awakened ones will return&the light of peace to the world...

ganonText: Oh! It's @.&I was expecting someone called Sheik.&Do you know what happened to them?
ganonHintText: Ha ha ha... You'll never beat me&by reflecting my lightning bolts&and unleashing the arrows from&%rDodongo's Cavern%w!^And even if you do, you'll never&find the legendary blade hidden in&%rShadow Temple%w!

sheikText: I overheard Ganondorf say that he&misplaced the %yLight Arrows%w in&%rDodongo's Cavern%w.^He also stole %gthe Master Sword%w&and hid it in %rShadow Temple%w.
dampeText: Whoever reads this, please enter&%rGoron City%w. I will let you&have my stretching, shrinking&keepsake.^I'm waiting for you.&--Dampé
gregText: By the way, if you're interested,&I saw the shiniest %gGreen Rupee%w&somewhere in%g the Lost Woods%w.^It's said to have %rmysterious&powers%w...^But then, it could just be another&regular rupee.&Oh well.
